    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a mechanically sound driver\u2019s car featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six with individual throttle bodies and a 7,900 RPM redline. It features the desirable 6-speed Getrag manual gearbox and a factory-spec limited-slip differential. To address platform-specific weak points, the rear subframe has been professionally reinforced and the VANOS system has been overhauled with upgraded seals. The suspension geometry remains precise with recently refreshed bushings. While the exterior shows minor road patina, the drivetrain is dialed-in, offering the tactile feedback and linear power delivery enthusiasts demand. Documented valve adjustments and cooling system refreshes ensure this chassis is track-ready or canyon-capable.",
