    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Up for sale is a well-maintained 2018 BMW 540i xDrive, finished in a sophisticated Sophisto Grey Metallic. This vehicle has been my reliable daily driver and has been kept in a climate-controlled garage. The exterior paint retains a deep gloss, though upon close inspection, you will find a few minor stone chips on the front fascia and a small scuff on the rear passenger-side alloy wheel. Inside, the Mocha Dakota leather interior is in excellent shape, showing no rips or significant bolster wear; the cabin remains a strict non-smoking environment and the dual-zone climate control blows ice cold. Every electronic component, from the navigation system to the premium Harmon Kardon audio, operates exactly as intended. Mechanically, the car is robust. I have adhered to a strict maintenance schedule with synthetic oil changes every 5,000 miles, and the front brakes were recently serviced. The tires are at approximately 70% tread life. I have a complete folder of service receipts to provide total peace of mind for the next owner. This is a dependable, high-quality luxury sedan that drives as beautifully as it looks.",
